comments: Adams (MEM) establishes himself in Barrett?s (NYK) path, firms up, and absorbs the contact to his front while setting the pick on the perimeter.
Brunson (NYK) reaches in and makes incidental hand on ball contact with Morant (MEM) as he cleanly dislodges the ball.
Morant (MEM) makes incidental contact to Hartenstein's (NYK) low body which results in him falling on top of Morant as both player pursue the loose ball. The contact that occurs is marginal.
Hartenstein (NYK) legally contests Bane?s (MEM) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Randle (NYK) extends his left arm into Aldama's (MEM) back, which dislodges him from his rebounding position. The contact affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Hartenstein (NYK) wraps his arm around Adams (MEM) and grabs his jersey during the rebound.
Adams (MEM) establishes himself in Brunson?s (NYK) path, firms up, and absorbs the contact while setting the pick on the perimeter.
Hartenstein (NYK) reaches in and makes contact to Morant's (MEM) off arm as he gathers and enters his upward shooting motion, during his running shot attempt.
Aldama (MEM) initiates contact with Randle?s (NYK) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Hartenstein (NYK) jumps vertically and absorbs the oncoming body contact during Morant?s (MEM) driving shot attempt.
Konchar (MEM) makes marginal contact to Brunson's (NYK) body that does not affect his SQBR in transition.
Konchar (MEM) legally contests Barrett?s (NYK) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Bane (MEM) initiates contact to Hartenstein's (NYK) lower body as he finish the play near the rim.
Randle (NYK) moves alongside Morant?s (MEM) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Fournier (NYK) establishes a screening position and then slightly turns as he initiates marginal contact with Roddy (MEM) during the off ball screen.
Brunson (NYK) moves into a legal position outside the restricted area in Morant's (MEM) path before Morant has started his upward motion.
Bane (MEM) brushes Reddish?s (NYK) arm and marginal contact occurs during Reddish?s (NYK) finish at the rim.
Morant's (MEM) shot attempt does make contact with the rim within the twenty four seconds allotted to his team.
Aldama (MEM) legally contests Reddish?s (NYK) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Hartenstein (NYK) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
While dribbling the ball up the sideline, Morant's (MEM) right foot steps out of bounds.
Hartenstein (NYK) commits a take foul on Jones (MEM). The contact that occurs to Jones' head/face is incidental.
Morant (MEM) commits a take foul on Brunson (NYK).
After Fournier (NYK) receives the inbound pass, he turns and his left foot steps out of bounds.
